The 8th Global Future Projects Forum and Exhibition 2026, organized by the Saudi Contractors Authority, will take place in Riyadh from December 7 to 10 at the Riyadh International Convention &amp; Exhibition Center. The event brings together contractors, stakeholders, and project owners from both the public and private sectors, offering a global platform to explore upcoming projects, understand application procedures, and engage with key industry leaders.

Featuring a comprehensive program that includes the main forum, an international exhibition, contracting excellence awards, a finance conference, and the annual meeting of the Confederation of International Contractors Association, the forum is expected to host over 400 local and international entities. It aims to enhance transparency, foster partnerships, support sector growth, and promote knowledge exchange in line with Saudi Vision 2030, while creating valuable networking opportunities across the construction and projects ecosystem.

Register Now

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

The Global Urban Festival (MIPIM – Le Marché International des Professionnels de l’Immobilier) is the world’s premier real estate gathering, connecting investors, developers, and cities to shape urban futures. Building on its flagship event in Cannes, MIPIM Middle East launches in Riyadh on 20–21 October 2026 as a 100% B2B platform focused on the region’s fast-paced growth and investment opportunities in sustainable urban development—bringing together international capital, policymakers, and leading developers through curated networking, strategic conference programming, premium showcases, and qualified one-to-one meetings, alongside exclusive Riyadh project tours to spotlight the Kingdom’s most significant developments.

Register Now

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

Under the patronage of the Custodian of the Two Holy Mosques King Salman bin Abdulaziz Al Saud, Riyadh will host the Global CSR Forum on 5–6 October, organized by the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Development, bringing together ministers, decision-makers, experts, private-sector leaders, and international organizations to explore the latest global developments in corporate social responsibility, share best practices, and spotlight innovative solutions that support the UN Sustainable Development Goals. Building on the momentum of its inaugural edition, the forum serves as a platform for cross-sector dialogue and partnership—connecting government, private, and non-profit stakeholders—while showcasing leading local and international CSR and sustainability initiatives and strengthening Saudi Arabia’s growing leadership in social responsibility.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

Saudi Warehousing &amp; Logistics Expo runs from 30 August to 1 September 2026 at Riyadh Front Exhibition &amp; Conference Center, bringing together the Kingdom’s most influential supply chain leaders and solution providers to drive smarter, more efficient logistics. Focused on empowering efficiency across warehousing, transport, and end-to-end supply chains, the expo offers exhibitors direct access to key decision-makers, a high-visibility platform to showcase and launch innovations, and targeted networking that supports business growth aligned with Vision 2030’s logistics transformation goals.

Register Now

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

The Esports World Cup 2026 returns to Riyadh from 6 July to 23 August, delivering a summer-long celebration of elite competition and live entertainment as top clubs and players battle across multiple genres and platforms. With a lineup spanning tactical shooters, MOBAs, fighting games, strategy, racing, and even chess—including global favourites such as League of Legends, Counter-Strike 2, Fortnite, and Rocket League—the festival reinforces Riyadh’s role as a leading hub for international esports. New for 2026, Trackmania joins the programme, bringing high-precision racing where competitors chase the fastest times on one of esports’ most skill-intensive stages.

The Esports World Cup, a multi-game global esports tournament and festival, will unite the global e-gaming community, including players, fans, game producers, and publishers, with a focus on fostering connections and collaborations.

&nbsp;

IN ACT returns to Riyadh with an electrifying night of immersive sound and high-energy performances at JAX District on May 8, 2026. Headlined by global dance music icon Carl Cox, alongside Dish Dash, Eyad, Hifi, Majid, and Vinyl Mode, the event promises a dynamic atmosphere driven by powerful beats and cutting-edge production. Taking place at Plot K, JAX District, this edition of IN ACT brings together music enthusiasts for an unforgettable experience in the heart of the capital.

Book Now

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

At Boulevard World in Riyadh, the Swimming with Dolphins experience offers kids a rare opportunity to connect with these intelligent and playful creatures up close. They can swim, interact, and learn about dolphin behavior. Perfect for marine-life enthusiasts, this experience combines fun, education, and wonder—making it one of the most memorable highlights of Riyadh Season.

Book Now

&nbsp;

Enter the eerie world of Midnight Manor at Boulevard World, Riyadh — a spine-chilling experience where mystery and suspense come alive. As the clock strikes midnight, step through red doors into dark corridors filled with haunting surprises and a host who awaits with a sinister smile. A thrilling adventure for those who dare, Midnight Manor is one of Riyadh Season’s most unforgettable horror attractions.

Book Now

&nbsp;

At Boulevard World in Riyadh, CoComelon Playdate invites families to step into the colorful and joyful world of CoComelon for an unforgettable interactive experience. Children can meet their favorite characters, JJ and Cody, while exploring hands-on activities designed to inspire learning, creativity, and fun. With engaging play zones and themed adventures, little ones can sing, play, and discover in a safe, imaginative environment—making it a perfect outing for families to create lasting memories together during Riyadh Season.

Book Now

&nbsp;

Step into Meta World, an immersive virtual reality experience within BLVD World that pushes the boundaries of imagination and technology. Designed for thrill-seekers and gaming enthusiasts alike, Meta World offers an unparalleled adventure through cutting-edge VR simulations, including The Climbing VR, Music VR Stand, and the VR Roller-Coaster Simulator. Each experience blends realism, excitement, and innovation—whether you're scaling virtual heights, moving to rhythmic beats, or racing through exhilarating worlds. Meta World invites you to explore limitless digital realms, test your skills, and connect with a community of gamers in an extraordinary fusion of entertainment and technology.

Book Now

&nbsp;

Located in the War Zone at Boulevard World, Battle Kart offers a thrilling fusion of electric karting, video gaming, and augmented reality, creating a one-of-a-kind racing adventure. Drivers compete on dynamic, interactive tracks where digital effects and real-world driving merge for an adrenaline-packed experience. With multiple game modes, power-ups, and challenges, Battle Kart transforms traditional racing into an immersive competition of speed, skill, and strategy—making it a must-try attraction at Riyadh Season.

Book Now

&nbsp;

Located within the Africa Zone at Boulevard World, BLVD Forest returns this season with a captivating African-inspired setting that brings visitors closer to nature. Home to rare and exotic animals, the forest offers immersive and interactive wildlife experiences where guests can observe, learn, and connect with animals in beautifully designed habitats. Perfect for families and nature enthusiasts, BLVD Forest combines education, adventure, and discovery in one unforgettable experience at Riyadh Season.

Book Now

&nbsp;

Returning to Boulevard World in Riyadh, BLVD Dolphinarium brings audiences a captivating new show featuring playful dolphins and engaging performances for all ages. Visitors can enjoy interactive experiences, from taking memorable photos to participating in educational programs that highlight marine life and conservation. Combining entertainment with learning, BLVD Dolphinarium offers a fun-filled aquatic experience at the heart of Riyadh Season.

Book Now

